Selling newspapers! Selling newspapers!

784
00:40:04,880 --> 00:40:07,040
Look at the new issue of "New Youth"!

785
00:40:07,120 --> 00:40:09,200
New declaration for the paper!

786
00:40:09,280 --> 00:40:11,280
New political ideas!

787
00:40:11,360 --> 00:40:13,600
New social ideals!

788
00:40:14,080 --> 00:40:14,880
Read newspaper!

789
00:40:14,960 --> 00:40:16,320
Newspaper!

790
00:40:16,400 --> 00:40:18,480
Look at the newly published "New Youth"

791
00:40:18,720 --> 00:40:20,240
New declaration for the paper!

792
00:40:20,400 --> 00:40:21,520
Please have one, sir.

793
00:40:22,240 --> 00:40:23,920
Newspaper!

794
00:40:24,080 --> 00:40:26,240
Look at the newly published "New Youth"!

795
00:40:32,560 --> 00:40:33,200
Please.

796
00:40:34,880 --> 00:40:35,360
Mr. Cai

797
00:40:35,600 --> 00:40:36,000
Mr. Zhongfu is here.

798
00:40:37,680 --> 00:40:38,080
Mr. Zhongfu.

799
00:40:38,160 --> 00:40:38,560
Master Cai.

800
00:40:39,120 --> 00:40:39,440
Come.

801
00:40:39,520 --> 00:40:39,920
You wanted to see me.

802
00:40:40,160 --> 00:40:40,800
Please sit down.

803
00:40:41,440 --> 00:40:41,680
Brother Zhongfu.

804
00:40:41,840 --> 00:40:42,320
Shizhi.

805
00:40:42,640 --> 00:40:43,760
Come, come, sit here.

806
00:40:46,160 --> 00:40:46,880
Okay.

807
00:40:52,240 --> 00:40:54,160
Zhang Shizhao sent a telegram.

808
00:40:54,400 --> 00:40:55,920
I wanted to send it to you.

809
00:40:56,400 --> 00:40:58,720
But I was talking business with Shizhi, couldn't find the time.

810
00:40:58,800 --> 00:41:00,320
So I invited you here.

811
00:41:01,440 --> 00:41:02,240
Take a look.

812
00:41:04,720 --> 00:41:08,080
Xingyan sent this from Guangdong.

813
00:41:08,720 --> 00:41:12,160
He is now the general secretary in the southern government.

814
00:41:12,480 --> 00:41:14,240
He's also the representative of this North-South peace talks.

815
00:41:14,880 --> 00:41:15,680
He said that

816
00:41:16,000 --> 00:41:17,680
the Southern government has approved

817
00:41:17,760 --> 00:41:18,960
Chen Jiongming's plan,

818
00:41:19,840 --> 00:41:22,160
they will start to work on establishing Southwest University.

819
00:41:22,640 --> 00:41:25,920
Zhang Shizhao and some others

820
00:41:26,160 --> 00:41:28,720
along with us two are entrusted as the one responsible for

821
00:41:29,520 --> 00:41:32,640
the establishment plan for the Southwest University.

822
00:41:33,280 --> 00:41:34,320
Zhang Shizhao said

823
00:41:34,880 --> 00:41:36,240
he wants you to

824
00:41:36,720 --> 00:41:38,400
go to Shanghai to meet him,

825
00:41:38,640 --> 00:41:40,000
then go to Guangzhou.
